史奈德首先選定[[阿曼達·塞佛瑞|阿曼達·塞佛瑞]]來擔任主角「洋娃娃」。<ref name="lessons">{{cite news | title = 'Watchmen' director goes for 'Sucker Punch' | date = 2009-03-04 | url = http://www.zap2it.com/movies/news/zap-watchmen-director-plans-next-project,0,1805690.story | accessdate = 2009-05-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090707225857/http://www.zap2it.com/movies/news/zap-watchmen-director-plans-next-project%2C0%2C1805690.story | archivedate = 2009年7月7日 | df =  }}</ref> 史奈德在詢問阿曼達是否願意出演此角色曾說，「可以看見我們嘗試著…她相當合適。假若她能出演那是再好不過了。」<ref name="CastingNews">{{cite news| last=Sanchez| first=Stephanie| title=IESB Exclusive: Zack Snyder's SUCKER PUNCH Casting News!| date=2009-02-23| url=http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=6348&Itemid=99| accessdate=2009-05-05| archive-date=2009-02-27| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090227065820/http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=6348&Itemid=99| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Zack Snyder Wants to 'Sucker Punch' Amanda Seyfried |date=2009-02-23 |url=http://www.getthebigpicture.net/blog/2009/2/24/zack-snyder-wants-to-sucker-punch-amanda-seyfried.html |accessdate=2009-05-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090226072236/http://www.getthebigpicture.net/blog/2009/2/24/zack-snyder-wants-to-sucker-punch-amanda-seyfried.html |archivedate=2009-02-26 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| last=Rich| first=Katy| title=Zack Snyder Wants Amanda Seyfried For Sucker Punch| date=2009-02-14| url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Zack-Snyder-Wants-Amanda-Seyfried-For-Sucker-Punch-12130.html| accessdate=2009-05-12| archive-date=2019-11-30| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130171701/https://www.cinemablend.com/new/Zack-Snyder-Wants-Amanda-Seyfried-For-Sucker-Punch-12130.html| dead-url=no}}</ref> 史奈德也曾提供此角給[[艾比·柯妮許|艾比·柯妮許]]、[[伊雯·瑞秋·伍德|伊雯·瑞秋·伍德]]、[[艾瑪·史東|艾瑪·史東]]和[[凡妮莎·哈金斯|凡妮莎·哈金斯]]。<ref>{{cite news|last=Elfman|first=Malin|title=Zack Snyder Goes for All Female Cast in Sucker Punch|url=http://screencrave.com/2009-03-04/zack-snyder-goes-for-all-female-cast-in-sucker-punch/|accessdate=2009-05-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110726074121/http://screencrave.com/2009-03-04/zack-snyder-goes-for-all-female-cast-in-sucker-punch/|archivedate=2011-07-26}}</ref> 儘管史奈德目標要她飾演洋娃娃的角色，但因電影和[[HBO|HBO]]影集《Big Love》的行程上衝突，女演員最後放棄演出機會。<ref name="Seyfried">{{cite news | last = Sperling | first = Nicole | title = Amanda Seyfried out of Zack Snyder's 'Sucker Punch' | work = [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 2009-03-23 | url = http://insidemovies.ew.com/2009/03/23/amanda-seyfried/ | accessdate = 2009-05-04 | archive-date = 2012-09-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120915105506/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2009/03/23/amanda-seyfried/ | dead-url = no }}</ref> 幾天後，艾蜜莉·布朗寧意願取代阿曼達演出洋娃娃角色。她的加入證實期間，凡妮莎、伊雯、艾比和史東皆仍在商討中。<ref name="Baby Doll" />

伊雯·瑞秋·伍德由於她在HBO的《[[噬血真愛|噬血真愛]]》的常駐演出，以及她的音樂劇《蜘蛛人：終結黑暗》（Spider-Man: Turn Off the Dark）和電影的拍攝行程衝突而退出徵選。<ref>[http://www.hollyscoop.com/movies/evan-rachel-wood/evan-rachel-wood-drops-out-of-film-to-star-in-spider-man_1543.aspx Evan Rachel Wood Drops Out of Film to Star in Spider-Man - Evan Rachel Wood<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090614045413/http://www.hollyscoop.com/movies/evan-rachel-wood/evan-rachel-wood-drops-out-of-film-to-star-in-spider-man_1543.aspx |date=2009-06-14 }}</ref> 吉娜·馬隆而後取代她飾演「火箭女」的角色。<ref>[http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i5d08aae04387a06d36176d0c40146ca6 Zack Snyder adds two to 'Sucker Punch!'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i5d08aae04387a06d36176d0c40146ca6 |date=20100810190349 }} (April 20, 2009)</ref> 鍾潔米簽下出演「琥珀姬」的角色，原本推測是選定史東來詮釋。<ref name="True Blood"/><ref name="Asylum" /> 飾演精神病院治療師「葛絲基夫人」的卡拉·裘吉諾，先前曾與史奈德的《[[守護者|守護者]]》合作過。<ref>{{cite news|last=Fleming|first=Michael|title=Gugino feels Snyder's 'Sucker Punch'|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118006839.html?categoryid=13&cs=1|accessdate=2009-08-04|date=2009-08-03|archive-date=2010-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100723014622/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118006839.html?categoryid=13&cs=1|dead-url=no}}</ref> 喬·漢姆在2009年8月末證實出演「浪子」一角。奧斯卡·伊薩克在同期也被指定雀選。<ref name="oscar" /><ref>{{cite web|last=Schwartz|first=Terri|title=Jon Hamm & Oscar Isaac Join Girl-Heavy Cast (Vanessa Hudgens! Emily Browning!) Of 'Sucker Punch'|work=MTV|date=2009-08-28|url=http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2009/08/28/jon-hamm-oscar-isaac-join-girl-heavy-cast-vanessa-hudgens-emily-browning-of-sucker-punch/|accessdate=2009-08-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090831104242/http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2009/08/28/jon-hamm-oscar-isaac-join-girl-heavy-cast-vanessa-hudgens-emily-browning-of-sucker-punch|archivedate=2009-08-31}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Rosenberg|first=Adam|title='Mad Men' Star Jon Hamm Takes A 'Sucker Punch' From Zack Snyder|work=MTV|date=2009-08-19|url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/08/19/mad-men-star-jon-hamm-takes-a-sucker-punch-from-zack-snyder/|accessdate=2009-08-29|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905120109/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/08/19/mad-men-star-jon-hamm-takes-a-sucker-punch-from-zack-snyder/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

