== 評價 ==
《殺客同萌》得到廣泛負面的電影評價。影評網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]182評論中僅有22%給于本片正面評價。<ref name="rottentomatoes.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sucker-punch-2010 |title=Sucker Punch Movie Reviews, Pictures |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=April 6, 2011 |archive-date=2021-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210402152044/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sucker-punch-2010 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 截至2011年4月6日，評論網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]的29篇影評裡，100分平均得到33，顯示“普遍不優”的評價。<ref>[http://www.metacritic.com/movie/sucker-punch Sucker Punch] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/67QSZFJKX?url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/sucker-punch |date=20120505051514 |dateformat=iso }}. ''[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]'', retrieved April 16, 2011</ref> 導演史奈德本身表明他想要本片“不僅僅只像電玩遊戲，而是個不受拘束且超嗨酷炫的故事”<ref name="ZackSnyder">{{cite news |title =Interview: Zack Snyder: The Watchman of "300" |date =2007-03-08 |url =http://www.the-trades.com/article.php?id=5288 |accessdate =2009-05-10 |deadurl =yes |archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20100314224926/http://www.the-trades.com/article.php?id=5288 |archivedate =2010-03-14 }}</ref>，部分影評仍是拿電玩和本電影作負面的比較。Richard Roeper給于本片Ｄ，並說本片「證明了一部華麗喧鬧、動作豐富且充滿艷麗美少女的電影－還是能夠無聊到流淚。」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.richardroeper.com/reviews/suckerpunch.aspx |title=''Sucker Punch'' |author=Roeper, Richard |date=2011-03-25 |accessdate=2011-03-26 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118010603/http://www.richardroeper.com/reviews/suckerpunch.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref> Orlando Sentinel僅給電影一星並稱其為「一點也不情色刺激的情色刺激電玩展示片。」<ref>{{cite web|title=Movie Review: Sucker Punch|url=http://blogs.orlandosentinel.com/entertainment_movies_blog/2011/03/movie-review-sucker-punch.html?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+entertainment%2Fmovies%2Fmovieblog+%28Frankly+My+Dear+-+Movies%29|publisher=Orlando Sentinel|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120124112317/http://blogs.orlandosentinel.com/entertainment_movies_blog/2011/03/movie-review-sucker-punch.html?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+entertainment%2Fmovies%2Fmovieblog+%28Frankly+My+Dear+-+Movies%29|archivedate=2012-01-24}}</ref> The A.V. Club的Nathan Rabin寫道，「有著找出提示物品的任務、層次分明的關卡和接連不斷的動作，史奈德撞擊出爐的混合品感覺與其說是電影，還比較像不必要的電玩改編延展情節、精緻的遊戲預告片」<ref>Nathan Rabin: [http://www.avclub.com/articles/sucker-punch,53611/ "Sucker Punch"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.avclub.com/articles/sucker-punch,53611/ |date=20131110042610 }}. The A.V. Club, March 24, 2011]</ref> 

《殺客同萌》對女性的塑造也招來批評聲浪。影評稱本電影帶有[[女性貶抑|女性貶抑]]，其他則表示處理方式涉及性暴力。[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]的Michael Phillips認為「查克史奈德必須要知道在他這部製作虛情假意地聚集瀕臨[[性侵|性侵]]與暴力復仇情節，偽裝成女性自主權的童話故事並不會滿足任何人，除了他自己。」<ref>Michael Phillips. [http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/movies/sc-mov-0324-sucker-punch-20110324,0,3614830.column ''One man's fantasy is another's torture''.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/movies/sc-mov-0324-sucker-punch-20110324,0,3614830.column |date=20110528074818 }} Retrieved on April 6, 2011.</ref> St. Petersburg Times影評者Steve Persall發現最冒犯不悅的事實是這部電影「建議將女性物化能使她們更強。男性在影片中不管怎麼毆打、痛斥、騷擾或殺害這些女孩都能令人感到放心。稍等，史奈德說，同時片裡對女性的污辱也能讓你目不暇給。」<ref>Steve Persall. [http://www.tampabay.com/features/movies/review-this-sucker-punch-is-low-blow-indeed/1159608 ''Review: This 'Sucker Punch' is low blow indeed''.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tampabay.com/features/movies/review-this-sucker-punch-is-low-blow-indeed/1159608 |date=20160817153547 }} Retrieved on April 06, 2011.</ref> [[紐約時報|紐約時報]]的A.O. Scott稱本片為「[[厭女症|厭女症]]的幻想曲」披著「[[女權主義|女權主義]]的標籤」，並且電影處理性暴力也產生問題。 <ref>{{cite news|title='Sucker Punch review from A.O. Scott|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2011/03/25/movies/sucker-punch-from-zack-snyder-review.html?partner=rss&emc=rss|publisher=''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]''|accessdate=6 April 2011|date=2011-03-24|archive-date=2011-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110331023354/http://movies.nytimes.com/2011/03/25/movies/sucker-punch-from-zack-snyder-review.html?partner=rss&emc=rss|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[綜藝|綜藝]]的Peter Debruge認為本片「誤導女性自主的姿態，儘管明顯地用奇幻的飼料孵孕出13歲的女孩們」，且事實上電影裡的女孩「受到不斷被強姦或謀殺威脅陰影下」讓本片「極不合適年輕觀眾」。<ref>Peter Debruge. [http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117944882?refcatid=31 ''Sucker Punch''.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117944882?refcatid=31 |date=20121108031928 }} April 06, 2011.</ref> 然而，[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]的Betsy Sharkey認為本片並沒物化女性也沒展現女權，取而代之的是「驚人出乎意料的刺激－一個不完美、過長、無拘束且完全地喧鬧，透過這張門票我不會想錯過這個世界。」<ref>{{cite news|title=Movie Review: 'Sucker Punch'|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-et-sucker-punch-20110325,0,7702288.story|author=Betsy Sharkey|publisher=''[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]''|accessdate=6 April 2011|date=2011-03-25|archive-date=2014-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141223075729/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/mar/25/entertainment/la-et-sucker-punch-20110325|dead-url=no}}</ref>

